Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸腐于野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊断于利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心爱之人 且赴黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢小姐 因为我如此肥胖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要娶你这般细腰的女子才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我时常这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢小姐厌恶肥胖之人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 我们也学学弦之介大人与胧小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不住口 丈助 真没酒品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见朱绢小姐一脸为难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可糟了 像是稍稍喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真美味 腌得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与甲贺的相比别有风味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定是盐的缘故 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺所购之盐均产自赤穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是喜欢不妨带些回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面盐仓中还贮有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有备无患啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盐可是兵粮中不可或缺之物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助 不是让你小心慎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 无妨的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后再无需隐藏保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗 阵五郎 朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的 胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所言甚是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值此良机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请伊贺众看看我们练习的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那舞是准备在婚仪中才展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当日展现更精彩的技艺便可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技 权充伊贺甲贺和解之贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨以此笛此舞 愿世代永昌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您每次与胧小姐相见都在练习这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我与胧小姐相见时会做何事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 我可说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何问我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 请原谅丈助的无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是甲贺最容易得意忘形的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不必介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢也并不介怀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真是有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为甲贺人会更凶神恶煞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了胧小姐讲那些面相凶恶的伊贺众的糗事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越有亲近感了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想听多少我便说多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人若非亲近相处便不能互相了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 未见着在土岐岭遇到的那几位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来得有些晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然出言相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但终究还是难以接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 定非此等原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是无可奈何之事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚想必还有其他拒绝与我同席的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多花些时间 逐渐互相了解便可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甲贺卍谷一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你们伊贺锷隐一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方各怀可怖的忍法秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因长年宿怨而互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我之见实是愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 你我携手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩断束缚两族的铁链
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天地真正广阔 让风声回荡两谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已将丈助关进那间客屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 卷轴的事切勿告诉他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被胧小姐察觉便糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:09:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢 我们也出手试探一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳他们此刻应当取了将监性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可天膳大人让我等不可妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此更应有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 鹈殿丈助就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是铁板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特意用这种牢房想困住本大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死我也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没想到被朱绢讨厌到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别有居心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起那时的表情真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 为何垂下眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是累了吧 夜也深了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回房休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并…并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸很红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何背对着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么 我没听清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我对这样的弦之介大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 果然还是去休息为好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没治的木头人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之没事便好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不顾羞耻前来相会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚宴上因为顾及伊贺众人的眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助…阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你走岔了真是抱歉 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么逃离这房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个嘛 就是全凭满腔爱念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难对付的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你的心意也与我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就当一夜我的新娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人叹服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来较量一下忍术吧 丈助阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若输了就如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一夜你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会留情哦 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好歇息 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 朱绢在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿丈助 命丧于此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太无情了吧 朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若死了你要如何补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这死肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来胜负已分了 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就按我们说好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是胧小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真是太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实是在下教而不改 又对朱绢小姐拉拉扯扯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于把她惹火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请您对弦之介大人保密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 请莫要再做这样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下对敢国神社发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\a6}敢国神社：位于三重县上野市，祭神为伊贺的鼻祖敢国津命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知你是哪位 伊贺之人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配尔等心灵、难以断绝的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其根深蒂固 方才的晚宴上我已有切身体会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望你们能斩断陈年宿怨的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今应是我等携手共书历史新章之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否相信我和胧小姐 助我们一臂之力？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢 无论鹈殿大人的玩笑有多过火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动用忍术还是有些过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是盐仓…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅 请您原谅 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵五郎 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下来 阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请莫要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想刺杀弦之介大人是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 如此下去阵五郎阁下会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准帮他 朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才那杀气 她是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…给我水 给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看 这不是雨夜阵五郎阁下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:20:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你莫非是想以这副模样刺杀弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我…水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 说吧 雨夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今甲贺与伊贺即将和解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何还要杀弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水 给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你说 看 要多少水都有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与服…服部家的…不战之约解…解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 跟服部家的约定？然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 伊贺与甲贺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺与甲贺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺与伊贺的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法之争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 我是不会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺十人众之一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿丈助 命丧于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨雾笼罩的甲贺村落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶气自北方逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引领他们的是残忍的邪念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰然老木所思为何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇袭 那是忍者的常用之道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍谷的北之街头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今化为血之泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 basilisk 甲贺忍法帖
